<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section id="how-it-works">
  <div class="section-label">The pipeline</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Six steps from <em>idea</em> to live database</h2>
  <p class="section-body">No SQL expertise required. Describe your product in plain English — the skill handles entity design, normalization, provisioning, and code generation end-to-end.</p>

  <div class="pipeline reveal">
    <div class="pipe-step">
      <div class="pipe-num">01</div>
      <span class="pipe-icon">🧠</span>
      <h3>Entity Extraction</h3>
      <p>Claude reads your spec and identifies every actor, resource, transaction, relationship, and event before writing any SQL.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pipe-step">
      <div class="pipe-num">02</div>
      <span class="pipe-icon">📐</span>
      <h3>Schema Design</h3>
      <p>Full PostgreSQL DDL in 3NF — UUID PKs, proper FK policies, NUMERIC for money, TIMESTAMPTZ everywhere, and indexes on every FK.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pipe-step">
      <div class="pipe-num">03</div>
      <span class="pipe-icon">🗄️</span>
      <h3>Database Creation</h3>
      <p>Creates the target database automatically from the business name. Every DDL statement uses IF NOT EXISTS so re-runs never crash.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pipe-step">
      <div class="pipe-num">04</div>
      <span class="pipe-icon">🌱</span>
      <h3>Realistic Seed Data</h3>
      <p>100–500 rows of coherent, domain-accurate data. Real names, realistic prices, valid FK references via CTEs — not user1@test.com.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pipe-step">
      <div class="pipe-num">05</div>
      <span class="pipe-icon">📊</span>
      <h3>Analytics Queries</h3>
      <p>6–10 labeled, ready-to-run queries covering revenue, funnels, top performers, anomalies, and operational monitoring.</p>
